org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.application
Class ListEpicActionsActivity

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.core.ApplicationActivity
          org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.application.ListEpicActionsActivity

public class ListEpicActionsActivity
extends ApplicationActivity

Lists the epic actions that can be performed by the device. This class implements the epic action 'org.epic.action.ListActions'. It accepts two different (optional) data extras: The integer 'start' is the index where to start the listing. The default for 'start' is 0. The integer 'size' is the maximum size that shall be retrieved (e.g., start = 10, size=5 lists a maximum of 5 epic actions starting with the entry with index 10). The default for 'size' is 10.
